        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer48754691" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer13906635756298754993">This is another Grandma Price reccomendation. I relied on her wide reading to guide me to wholesome books. <br/><br/>These are fun mysteries, short, intriguing, easy to read that take you back centuries ago to medieval monestaries during the feudal system. A real slice of life at that time too.<br/><br/>There are many books in this Brother Cadafel series. All are good. Some characters you run into time and again.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


