<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/57351600-the-vanishing-children"><img alt="The Vanishing Children (Master Mercurius Mysteries, #5)" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1615226716l/57351600._SX98_.jpg" />
